description: Denver Wilson and Paul Majors are relaxing and browsing through AllBoy magazines.When Denver announces that he should try out to be a model, Paul just laughs at him.  That is,until Denver whips out his thick, stiff boner!  Paul's mouth is like a magnet for that prize untilGeorge Plozen enters the room and offers his even bigger 9-incher for them to worship.
title: PonyBoy: HorsePlay
